# Exercise 1.1 — American scientists.
#
# Write a query below that lists the name and birth year of every
# person born in the US. The loader picks up person.csv from this
# directory.
#
# Hint: one of the three arguments to `person(...)` should be a
# string literal; the other two should be variables.

extensional person(name: string, country: string, year_born: integer).

